name: Get Hardware And BIOS Information
description: Returns detailed information concerning the Graphics Processing Unit (GPU) and RAM installed on the device. Additionally, the script obtains the serial numbers and types of the installed disks, as well as the BIOS version and release date.

outputs.description: Name of the graphics card installed on the device
outputs.name: GPUName

outputs.description: Provider of the graphics card driver
outputs.name: GPUDriverVendor

outputs.description: Version of the graphics card driver
outputs.name: GPUDriverVersion

outputs.description: For each installed disk drive, the number allocated by the manufacturer to identify the physical media and its type (HDD/SDD)
outputs.name: DiskSerialNumberAndType

outputs.description: Total number of memory slots available on the device
outputs.name: TotalRAMSlots

outputs.description: Maximum total amount of RAM that can be installed on the device
outputs.name: MaximumRAM

outputs.description: Number of memory slots currently used
outputs.name: UsedRAMSlots

outputs.description: Amount of RAM currently installed
outputs.name: InstalledRAM

outputs.description: Capacity of each installed memory bank
outputs.name: RAMBankCapacity

outputs.description: For each installed memory bank, label of the socket or circuit board that holds the memory
outputs.name: RAMBankDeviceLocator

outputs.description: For each installed memory bank, implementation form factor for the chip
outputs.name: RAMBankFormFactor

outputs.description: For each installed bank, name of the organization responsible for producing the physical element
outputs.name: RAMBankManufacturer

outputs.description: For each installed bank, part number assigned by the organization responsible for producing or manufacturing the physical element
outputs.name: RAMBankPartNumber

outputs.description: For each installed bank, manufacturer-allocated number to identify the physical element
outputs.name: RAMBankSerialNumber

outputs.description: For each installed memory bank, speed of the physical memory, in nanoseconds
outputs.name: RAMBankSpeed

outputs.description: For each installed memory bank, configured voltage for this device, in millivolts
outputs.name: RAMBankVoltage

outputs.description: For each installed memory bank, total width, in bits, of the physical memory, including check or error correction bits
outputs.name: RAMBankTotalWidth

outputs.description: BIOS version installed on the device obtained from the registry
outputs.name: RegistryBIOSVersion

outputs.description: BIOS version installed on the device obtained from the WMI Object 'Win32_BIOS'
outputs.name: ManagementBiosVersion

outputs.description: BIOS release date installed on the device
outputs.name: BIOSDate
